This project integrates Chatwoot with AI-powered responses for hoteliers.  
It helps hotels reply faster to guest queries and manage bookings better.  

### Features
- Auto-reply to WhatsApp / Website / Instagram messages
- Connect with Chatwoot inbox
- Customizable hotel FAQs
- AI-powered responses (using OpenAI API)

